<span id="Description"></span>
== Beschreibung ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
'''CSV2Objects''' generates large batches of 3D objects with text driven by CSV files.
It uses horizontal guide lines in a sketch to position text, creates ShapeStrings,
extrudes them, and optionally fuses the result with a target solid. It supports batch
export to STL, 3MF, and STEP.
</div>

